296
00:14:04,760 --> 00:14:06,440
Get in and get out?

297
00:14:06,440 --> 00:14:07,640
That means you're visiting.

298
00:14:07,799 --> 00:14:09,679
Okay. Then we'll get the tickets.

299
00:14:10,119 --> 00:14:11,960
Come visit tomorrow.

300
00:14:12,119 --> 00:14:13,679
(Open to the public from 9 a.m. to late night)
We're closed for today.

301
00:14:13,960 --> 00:14:14,599
Then,

302
00:14:14,640 --> 00:14:15,960
get Su Lie and Luo Ke out here.

303
00:14:16,000 --> 00:14:17,000
