316
00:14:37,080 --> 00:14:37,880
Here.

317
00:14:39,559 --> 00:14:42,520
Kele does know
how to do things, doesn't she?

318
00:14:42,799 --> 00:14:43,840
Scan this.

319
00:14:45,119 --> 00:14:46,000
You should eat something good.

320
00:14:46,000 --> 00:14:47,239
Take a break. Have a late-night snack.

321
00:14:47,359 --> 00:14:51,400
Well... Welcome to
the family of Yao Inc.!

322
00:14:51,960 --> 00:14:52,479
Please.

323
00:14:52,479 --> 00:14:53,479
Welcome.

324
00:14:53,479 --> 00:14:55,039
A warm welcome.

325
00:14:55,960 --> 00:14:58,239
Bro, did I do it well this time?

326
00:14:59,280 --> 00:15:01,919
Those tourist ladies were so nice.

327
00:15:02,000 --> 00:15:03,400
Even though
they've never lived in a big house,

328
00:15:03,559 --> 00:15:04,799
