in a tourist attraction!

365
00:16:18,719 --> 00:16:20,359
Xu Guanghan really
knows how to make money, huh?

366
00:16:20,520 --> 00:16:21,960
We weren't rehired.

367
00:16:22,359 --> 00:16:23,640
We're here to get you guys out of here.

368
00:16:23,840 --> 00:16:25,280
