454
00:19:47,040 --> 00:19:48,719
I think I can let it go now.

455
00:19:51,920 --> 00:19:52,680
All right.

456
00:19:52,800 --> 00:19:53,560
Let's not talk about

457
00:19:53,560 --> 00:19:55,079
