00:23:35,119 --> 00:23:37,119
companies that run social software.

558
00:23:37,199 --> 00:23:39,079
But why did yours fail
when theirs did not?

559
00:23:39,920 --> 00:23:41,040
That's because Qianya stood up

560
00:23:41,040 --> 00:23:42,479
against Xu Guanghan.

561
00:23:44,959 --> 00:23:46,239
If it's not the world that's wrong,

562
00:23:46,439 --> 00:23:47,760
it's your competitor.

563
00:23:48,280 --> 00:23:50,680
You are as laughable as they say.

564
00:23:51,520 --> 00:23:53,439
If someone who keeps failing,

565
00:23:53,560 --> 00:23:55,479
just keeps finding excuses,

566
00:23:56,040 --> 00:23:56,920
they won't succeed

567
00:23:56,920 --> 00:23:57,920
no matter what they do.

568
00:23:59,640 --> 00:24:01,000
Aren't you in a rush?

569
00:24:01,400 --> 00:24:03,199
If you aren't interested,

570
00:24:04,000 --> 00:24:04,880
you can leave.

571
00:24:05,680 --> 00:24:06,920
Guan Qianya,

572
00:24:07,439 --> 00:24:10,439
where does
all that pride of yours come from?

573
00:24:10,599 --> 00:24:12,959
I did my research before I came.

574
00:24:13,680 --> 00:24:14,599
Your company's done for.

575
00:24:14,680 --> 00:24:15,959
You lost your house and your car.

576
00:24:15,959 --> 00:24:17,280
You'd probably
have to sleep in the streets soon.

577
00:24:17,839 --> 00:24:19,439
You want to start over
with these slides?

578
00:24:19,880 --> 00:24:21,800
Not likely possible.
Stop wasting your time.

579
00:24:22,239 --> 00:24:23,560
Let me tell you this.

580
00:24:24,000 --> 00:24:24,719
You've long been

581
00:24:24,719 --> 00:24:26,439
blacklisted among investors.

582
00:24:26,959 --> 00:24:27,479
Of course,

583
00:24:28,199 --> 00:24:30,599
I don't care how many
investors you've met before this,

584
00:24:30,800 --> 00:24:32,640
but those who are still
willing to meet you

585
00:24:32,920 --> 00:24:33,719
are either

586
00:24:34,319 --> 00:24:35,640
ones with ulterior motives

587
00:24:35,680 --> 00:24:37,160
or newbies in the investment business.

588
00:24:37,359 --> 00:24:39,520
Then which one are you?

589
00:24:41,040 --> 00:24:42,319
As a businesswoman,

590
00:24:42,400 --> 00:24:44,079
I'm here to give you a piece of advice.

591
00:24:45,199 --> 00:24:46,839
Stop embarrassing yourself.

592
00:24:48,319 --> 00:24:49,439
That's all I have to say.

593
00:24:50,920 --> 00:24:53,400
And that's five minutes. See you.

594
00:25:02,439 --> 00:25:04,319
It's okay. We still have chances.

595
00:25:14,719 --> 00:25:15,880
Goodbye.

596
00:25:16,079 --> 00:25:16,800
Bye.

597
00:25:24,920 --> 00:25:26,119
What is it, Lu Xiao?

598
00:25:26,439 --> 00:25:28,640
Boss, I have something to tell you.

599
00:25:28,800 --> 00:25:29,560
Speak.

600
00:25:32,400 --> 00:25:33,239
I want to quit.

601
00:25:33,400 --> 00:25:34,239
Why?

602
00:25:34,439 --> 00:25:36,760
Is the pay not high enough?

603
00:25:37,680 --> 00:25:40,640
Were you approached by other studios?

604
00:25:41,760 --> 00:25:42,760
Now, I'm curious.

605
00:25:42,760 --> 00:25:44,040
Why do you want to quit?

606
00:25:44,520 --> 00:25:46,000
Because during the class today,

607
00:25:46,199 --> 00:25:47,160
that girl...

608
00:25:47,680 --> 00:25:49,280
Your move here was...

609
00:25:55,439 --> 00:25:56,680
You want to quit

610
00:25:56,680 --> 00:25:57,920
just because of that?

611
00:25:58,199 --> 00:25:59,359
It's not a small matter.

612
00:25:59,520 --> 00:26:00,599
It's harassment.

613
00:26:00,800 --> 00:26:02,479
What sort of harassment?

614
00:26:02,680 --> 00:26:04,640
You're the instructor,
and she's the student.

615
00:26:04,760 --> 00:26:05,640
It's perfectly normal

616
00:26:05,640 --> 00:26:07,839
to have physical contact
when you're teaching her to dance.

617
00:26:07,880 --> 00:26:09,439
You're thinking too much into it.

618
00:26:09,719 --> 00:26:10,680
Our female students

619
00:26:10,680 --> 00:26:11,800
are all good students.

620
00:26:11,839 --> 00:26:13,000
They wouldn't do something like this.

621
00:26:13,400 --> 00:26:14,439
There's another thing as well.

622
00:26:14,880 --> 00:26:16,880
Mr. Lu,
I have something to tell you.

623
00:26:17,439 --> 00:26:18,199
Go ahead.

624
00:26:18,640 --> 00:26:19,560
Come closer.

625
00:26:21,800 --> 00:26:22,560
Closer.

626
00:26:22,599 --> 00:26:23,640
Just tell me. I'm listening.

627
00:26:24,119 --> 00:26:24,959
Come closer.

628
00:26:31,880 --> 00:26:33,400
That's a small matter too.

629
00:26:33,400 --> 00:26:34,640
You call that a small matter too?

630
00:26:34,719 --> 00:26:36,800
All she did was give you
a peck on the cheek.

631
00:26:36,800 --> 00:26:39,119
She's just kissing goodbye.

632
00:26:39,119 --> 00:26:40,880
If you're not used to it,

633
00:26:40,880 --> 00:26:42,880
I can help you practice it every day.

634
00:26:43,400 --> 00:26:44,680
That way, you'll get used to it.

635
00:26:44,839 --> 00:26:45,560
No need.

636
00:26:46,319 --> 00:26:48,359
All right. Go back to work then.

637
00:26:49,359 --> 00:26:51,079
What? Is there something else?

638
00:26:53,160 --> 00:26:54,119
Mr. Lu,

639
00:26:54,359 --> 00:26:55,760
are you free after class?

640
00:26:55,880 --> 00:26:57,719
Let's have dinner together.

641
00:26:58,160 --> 00:26:59,000
Sorry.

642
00:26:59,119 --> 00:27:00,280
I have something to do after work.

643
00:27:00,479 --> 00:27:02,800
What could be more important than work?

644
00:27:02,959 --> 00:27:05,439
If you promise to have dinner with me,

645
00:27:05,599 --> 00:27:07,800
I'll take care of your
KPI for this month.

646
00:27:08,599 --> 00:27:11,560
If you go to a bar with me...

647
00:27:11,719 --> 00:27:13,439
I'll have you covered
for the next six months.

648
00:27:14,119 --> 00:27:15,520
Sorry. You came to the wrong person.

649
00:27:15,839 --> 00:27:17,800
I have no obligation to go out with you.

650
00:27:18,839 --> 00:27:20,239
What are you acting
all pure and noble for?

651
00:27:20,239 --> 00:27:21,800
Who do you think you are?

652
00:27:21,839 --> 00:27:24,280
If the people like you,
then you're a celebrity instructor.

653
00:27:24,359 --> 00:27:25,359
But without them,

654
00:27:25,359 --> 00:27:26,680
you're nothing.

655
00:27:27,199 --> 00:27:28,719
I'm going to see your boss right now.

656
00:27:28,719 --> 00:27:30,239
I'm going to cancel my membership!

657
00:27:31,680 --> 00:27:33,400
Well, that's not funny.

658
00:27:33,439 --> 00:27:35,520
You think she crossed the line, too,
don't you?

659
00:27:35,640 --> 00:27:37,760
I think you're socially inept!

660
00:27:37,920 --> 00:27:39,719
It's just dinner and a drink.

661
00:27:39,839 --> 00:27:41,079
What's the big deal?
You've got nothing to lose.

662
00:27:41,079 --> 00:27:43,079
Can't you treat a client as a friend?

663
00:27:43,160 --> 00:27:43,640
But she...

664
00:27:43,640 --> 00:27:44,680
What's with the "but"?

665
00:27:44,760 --> 00:27:47,040
You need to understand
what it means to work with clients.

666
00:27:47,040 --> 00:27:47,640
Understand?

667
00:27:47,680 --> 00:27:49,079
If you get along with your clients,

668
00:27:49,160 --> 00:27:50,359
your KPI will go up.

669
00:27:50,359 --> 00:27:52,199
If your KPI goes up,
then your bonus increases as well.

670
00:27:52,199 --> 00:27:53,599
Isn't that something good?

671
00:27:53,719 --> 00:27:55,439
I won't be happy if that's

672
00:27:55,520 --> 00:27:56,800
how my KPI goes up.

673
00:27:56,959 --> 00:27:58,839
If you insist
on keeping your principles,

674
00:27:59,040 --> 00:28:00,880
then I'm afraid this job isn't for you.

675
00:28:01,160 --> 00:28:03,000
With that attitude of yours,

676
00:28:03,000 --> 00:28:04,760
you won't last long
no matter where you work.

677
00:28:04,920 --> 00:28:06,680
If you can't even stand
a little pressure like this,

678
00:28:06,760 --> 00:28:08,680
then you should just go back
to your old life.

679
00:28:09,119 --> 00:28:10,280
In this world,

680
00:28:10,479 --> 00:28:12,640
no one is going
to give you something for nothing.

681
00:28:14,599 --> 00:28:16,599
Oh, there is someone who would.

682
00:28:16,920 --> 00:28:17,880
Xu Guanghan.

683
00:28:28,199 --> 00:28:30,119
Qianya, why don't we leave first?

684
00:28:31,520 --> 00:28:33,000
We still have another investor coming.

685
00:28:33,560 --> 00:28:35,479
We've been waiting for two hours.

686
00:28:35,839 --> 00:28:37,280
But I want to wait for them.

687
00:28:44,160 --> 00:28:46,599
Why don't I take you to a place?

688
00:28:47,599 --> 00:28:48,680
Where?

689
00:28:49,719 --> 00:28:51,000
A place you know well.

690
00:29:02,599 --> 00:29:03,839
Are you a student of ours?

691
00:29:03,839 --> 00:29:05,079
Or are you interested
in having classes?

692
00:29:05,439 --> 00:29:07,199
Oh, no. I'm here to pick up someone.

693
00:29:07,560 --> 00:29:09,199
Pick up someone? Who?

694
00:29:09,400 --> 00:29:11,239
Lu Xiao. I'm here to pick him up.

695
00:29:11,359 --> 00:29:12,439
If he isn't finished yet,

696
00:29:12,439 --> 00:29:13,719
I'll just wait over there.

697
00:29:13,880 --> 00:29:15,000
Don't bother.

698
00:29:15,040 --> 00:29:16,400
I fired him.

699
00:29:16,400 --> 00:29:17,800
Fired?

700
00:29:18,599 --> 00:29:20,319
Isn't he a celebrity instructor here?

701
00:29:20,439 --> 00:29:21,599
His dancing is great.

702
00:29:21,599 --> 00:29:22,800
Why would you fire him?

703
00:29:22,839 --> 00:29:25,079
Because he doesn't love this job enough.

704
00:29:25,160 --> 00:29:26,839
Because he doesn't know
how to deal with people.

705
00:29:26,839 --> 00:29:28,239
He doesn't know
how to deal with clients.

706
00:29:28,319 --> 00:29:30,079
He's not dedicated enough,
and neither is he crafty enough.

707
00:29:30,199 --> 00:29:31,439
Someone like him

708
00:29:31,439 --> 00:29:33,239
should just stay in the Bay House.

709
00:29:33,439 --> 00:29:35,119
It's not that easy to survive

710
00:29:35,119 --> 00:29:36,359
in the real world.

