00:30:36,970 --> 00:30:47,130
♪You and I have different memories♪

716
00:30:47,610 --> 00:30:53,010
♪As if we're searching
for the intersection♪

717
00:30:53,010 --> 00:31:00,810
♪Piecing together
the secrets of the future♪

718
00:31:01,610 --> 00:31:04,610
♪I'm falling hard♪

719
00:31:08,130 --> 00:31:14,490
♪Draw a circle to encircle our hearts♪

