00:31:15,410 --> 00:31:21,850
♪A heart for a heart♪

721
00:31:22,370 --> 00:31:28,490
♪Your favorite melody begins to play♪

722
00:31:29,090 --> 00:31:32,450
♪In my mind♪

723
00:31:32,570 --> 00:31:36,970
♪Beautiful memories
